Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请和我一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起疼痛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和我有着一样的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来把你送到家就准备离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个孩子不想离开你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在这个时间 我学会了你们的语言和文化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备整个星期天都睡觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么赶快去把脸洗洗然后吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面天气很好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个... 爸爸你现在不去工作可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好吃早餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一摸一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 黄油 奶油 巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杯子...还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 红茶在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你知道我家的东西放在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是红茶啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要对你好好说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如这个是太阳系第三行星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是地球 你住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边是我住的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个行星相距很远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说有多远的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之他们距离很远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说白了 我们不是地球人是从另一个星球来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你们的话来说 就是外星人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天 我们称其为玛基的生物囊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一种很危险的怪兽的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人偷走了 那个小偷逃上太空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋一共有六个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天 我们和其中的一个怪物战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在我的行星从事像你们的警察那样的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和同伴抓住了那个偷蛋的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些话你懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴把小偷带走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我在运那些蛋回我们行星的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一个蛋孵化出了怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它开始在内部破坏我的宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个原因我的飞船转移失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这个行星所在的星系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:08:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转移是扭曲时间和空间的一种特殊移动手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽量避免降落到地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是宇宙船坠毁了 而那些蛋也散落到别处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们昨天干掉一个 还有五个在这个北海道的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五个呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我一定会把它们全部干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个 我刚做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人 那个... 一定是电视的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在来说明一下这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是这个孩子的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是里贝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当和敌人战斗的时候可以作为盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单地说就是有智能和生命的金属
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天看到我用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当人使用过之后\N它会和使用者内心相通并拥有使用者的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到攻击时就会自动保护使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心相通同时拥有我的记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有与你一样的记忆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我知道厨房的东西在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也知道你的衣服在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的事情我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:10:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来从人体中分离出来会变回原来的样子\N至于为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也...完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情大概就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我能叫你小翼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就叫我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...对了就叫我光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这个人就叫他DD吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用这个行星的话来说 这个就最合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是妈妈对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次觉得心中好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？掉了一个陨石下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 有个目击者说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个红色的东西掉在你房子的后面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈...怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果陨石真的掉下来了 我还能站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么觉得 但是为了以防万一 我还是要去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯去吧 我泡了咖啡 回来的时候在这里坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些东西要拿 我想我要回去一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 能不能把你父亲的衣服借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以不用过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去外面看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把这个孩子也带上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为两个人一起比较有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无任何异常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神防避起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这个东西就能阻止他往前走\N是一种干扰心智的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为科学和文化不同\N所以我们暂时不想和地球有任何的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何的接触都是禁止的 所以我不能留下痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总会有人发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经求救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前 无论如何也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！ 花 这个是花吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有记忆但是 这个是实物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香 而且真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 那边还有更多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走得太远哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花...花...花...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 这么多花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 那边有漂亮的河 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛基的囊到底掉到那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果找不到的话会 很麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他们无法适应地球环境
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要松手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看是鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次见到 感动ing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为会掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼就是那棵树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你常常想起的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的记忆里经常出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真安静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么时候玛基会孵化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙船损毁 无法和同伴联络上 看来只能呆在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐！DD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些事情要问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我们的晚饭和信他一起吃如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸工作太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼一个人很孤单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一起吃的话比较热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸两个人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我也不喜欢和别人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为晚饭时间是和翼唯一在一起谈话的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是老鼠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么大的老鼠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看 爸爸就坐在这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉她不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是练习飞腿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 小声点 我一会就拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...我的书包从桌子上掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你在看什么 快点吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰箱门 要关好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就不需要带监视器了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 瞳孔的颜色也能变化呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想在这里引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么也应该改变下头发的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 根据调查染发的人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你现在要去城市对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头发太引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我没有改变的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我去买一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么气味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼用零用钱给你买的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颜色好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是长度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人留长头发的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 把剪子拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不作彻底不就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.93,0:22:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把头发扎成辫子 感觉会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记约定的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 走好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手续都已经办好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一能把基本的操作方法告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 操作方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.52,0:24:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼 干扰到工作了...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.92,0:24:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 这是我们刚烤出来的奶油面包 要尝尝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.96,0:24:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.85,0:25:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.01,0:25:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自出来不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.64,0:25:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的 大家都以为我是小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.60,0:25:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.52,0:25:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 时间快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.57,0:25:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.46,0:25:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了DD
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.13,0:25:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点上来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.68,0:25:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她也在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.18,0:25:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系这样比较好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.43,0:25:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 要在这里道别
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.18,0:25:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 马上道别？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.77,0:25:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.94,0:25:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能再给她添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.52,0:25:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.73,0:25:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再留在这里 我们的存在会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.36,0:25:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.07,0:26:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我们不能再给她带来危险
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.16,0:26:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.37,0:26:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮了我们不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.46,0:26:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.63,0:26:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 没...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.76,0:26:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会和小翼道别的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.01,0:26:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们不去买衣服是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.22,0:26:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.80,0:26:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些衣服是要还的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.02,0:26:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DD穿着小翼爸爸的衣服也要还的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.06,0:26:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.52,0:26:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.11,0:26:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼也一起去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.32,0:26:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.17,0:27:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了！ 到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.72,0:27:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.89,0:27:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要擅自乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.04,0:27:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里好多东西都是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.12,0:27:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.17,0:27:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 那边不错 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.40,0:28:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.15,0:28:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.61,0:28:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.99,0:28:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.78,0:28:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好看
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.12,0:28:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.87,0:28:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.46,0:28:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.33,0:28:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.08,0:28:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你穿的好看 我穿上也会和小翼一样好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.80,0:28:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.34,0:28:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该帮你自己选 而不是帮我选
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.55,0:28:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.05,0:28:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.85,0:28:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐们 你们的母亲在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.52,0:28:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.68,0:28:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有妈妈 不过有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.60,0:28:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那爸爸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.06,0:28:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今天不在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.86,0:28:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说你们迷路了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.03,0:28:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.53,0:28:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.45,0:28:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.74,0:28:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.03,0:28:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.75,0:28:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.33,0:28:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.21,0:28:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我付钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.54,0:29:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.17,0:29:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.01,0:29:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.72,0:29:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你觉得这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.39,0:29:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给DD惹麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.10,0:29:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.81,0:29:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有今天 才能和小翼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.49,0:29:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 椎名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.53,0:29:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 相泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.04,0:29:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名同学 你一个人购物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.66,0:29:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.17,0:29:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃！？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.79,0:29:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.42,0:29:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.92,0:29:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.01,0:29:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是她的妹妹 光
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.97,0:29:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.09,0:29:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名同学 原来是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.60,0:29:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.31,0:29:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去那边看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.02,0:29:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.81,0:29:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.19,0:30:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.27,0:30:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？ 被人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.69,0:30:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是你的同学 叫相泽对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.86,0:30:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的男孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.82,0:30:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再去看看其他的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.14,0:30:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.94,0:30:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要道别了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.61,0:30:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.53,0:30:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托小翼的福 我体验了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.87,0:31:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.08,0:31:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.38,0:31:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.79,0:31:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.96,0:31:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛基开始活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.42,0:31:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.48,0:32:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在这森林的对面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.02,0:32:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.86,0:32:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.61,0:32:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.67,0:32:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.25,0:32:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.00,0:32:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.69,0:32:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.95,0:33:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛基在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.45,0:33:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地下移动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.29,0:33:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适应的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.71,0:33:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.53,0:33:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比通常的玛基运动能力强很多
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.78,0:33:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是受到了这个行星环境的某种影响
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.17,0:33:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DD没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.96,0:34:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人还没有回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.15,0:34:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 快点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.19,0:34:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.11,0:35:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.61,0:35:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃！？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.58,0:35:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.38,0:35:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.14,0:35:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.44,0:35:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.03,0:35:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.63,0:35:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.55,0:35:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.77,0:36:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.15,0:36:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.57,0:36:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.08,0:36:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.83,0:36:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 这是你第一次叫我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.17,0:36:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.55,0:37:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它从下面来了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.23,0:37:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.40,0:37:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在该我们反击了 虽然很想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.61,0:37:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它在地下的速度实在太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.82,0:37:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么方法把它从地下赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.58,0:37:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它赶出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.12,0:37:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有高的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.12,0:37:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.46,0:38:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（高压输电塔）那是...那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.63,0:38:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好地方 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.09,0:38:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.80,0:38:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.63,0:38:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.98,0:38:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳上去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.77,0:38:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.20,0:38:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(生物反应接近)
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.74,0:38:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 在这里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.33,0:38:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃！？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.33,0:38:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请相信我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.88,0:38:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.73,0:39:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将力量集中在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.41,0:39:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.73,0:39:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(无生命反应)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.32,0:39:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.62,0:40:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DD
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.25,0:40:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 要分离了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.85,0:40:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DD 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.68,0:40:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛基呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.98,0:40:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我们干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.06,0:40:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.61,0:40:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.48,0:40:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.28,0:40:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里贝斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.66,0:40:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.08,0:40:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.75,0:40:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里贝斯 也是有生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.57,0:41:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你也该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.07,0:41:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.41,0:41:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.92,0:41:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌分开
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.46,0:41:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和小光在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.55,0:41:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.26,0:41:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.43,0:41:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.77,0:41:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？DD
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.56,0:41:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.03,0:41:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在增援来之前我只能依靠她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.28,0:42:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.28,0:42:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边的是翼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.91,0:42:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚了 我在到处找呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.21,0:42:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前没有告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.47,0:42:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一直住在阿姨家 翼的妹妹光
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.26,0:42:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.89,0:42:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来小翼有一个双胞胎的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.48,0:42:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.48,0:42:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友 摄影师 堂本大助
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.61,0:42:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.40,0:42:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拍摄北海道的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.82,0:42:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能叫他在这里住一段时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.53,0:42:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.66,0:42:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人越多越热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.53,0:42:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.83,0:42:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切结束的时候我就解除记忆控制
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.17,0:42:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.41,0:43:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 椎名翼的妹妹椎名光
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.20,0:43:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.99,0:45:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以双胞胎姐妹的身份一起生活的翼和光
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.17,0:45:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是翼没有光的开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.34,0:45:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且越来越没有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.80,0:45:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候和另一个玛基的战斗开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.51,0:45:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“我们必须同心才能打败它”
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.31,0:45:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.10,0:45:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在翼的心中不断的回响着
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.64,0:45:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试拿出勇气来
